data.description: New Price! Gated Entry Large Estate Home with Resort Pool and Spa made for entertaining and privacy. Fully updated kitchen. Luminous Entryway with office/5th bedroom/study off to the right. Walk through to impressive connection space  for entertaining. Upgraded Gourmet kitchen/espresso cabinets with Coffee Bar, propane range. Contemporary Island for including your family/Guests. Upstairs Luxurious owner's bedroom suite with sitting area and dual closets, master bath separate tub/shower. High ceilings throughout. Backyard covered porch and Stunning, Custom pool/spa. Large Lot.Privacy fence.
